prodNameC: 常盈人體生長激素酵素連結免疫分析組
ingredientsDesc:
Anti-hGH-Coated Microtitration Strips: One stripholder containing 96 microtitration wells coated with anti-hGH antibody.
hGH Standards: Lyophilized.
hGH Controls: Lyophilized.
Assay Buffer: containing a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
hGH Antibody-Enzyme Conjugate Concentrate: containing anti-hGH antibody conjugated to enzyme horseradish peroxidase in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
TMB Chromogen Solution: containing a solution of tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) in citrate buffer with hydrogen peroxide.
Wash Concentrate: containing buffered saline with a nonionic detergent.
Stopping Solution: containing 0.2 M sulfuric acid.
